[*  Copyright 2026 Jack Henry and Associates
**
**  PowerOn Name:                     BANNO.LOANPAYMENT.SKIP.V2.POW
**  Configuration Letterfile Name:    BANNO.LOANPAYMENT.SKIP.V2.CFG
**
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**  Program Summary
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**  This Banno service PowerOn allow the user to select one or more
**  eligible loans and, for a fee, have the loan due date advanced
**  by 28 days, 1 month or one payment cycle, depending upon the
**  parameter settings. Once the new due date has been calculated, the
**  loan maturity date will also be advanced accordingly.
**
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**  Program states and JSON returns
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**    STATE:  GETPRELOADDATA
**  PROCESS:  Process GETPRELOADDATA state and create json response
**     PASS:  @RGUSERCHR1 n/a
**            @RGUSERNUM1 n/a
**   RETURN:  Provides UX GETPRELOADDATA response
**
**    STATE:  PERFORMSKIPAPAYMENT
**  PROCESS:  Process PERFORMSKIPAPAYMENT state and create json response
**     PASS:  @RGUSERCHR1 Comma-separated list of loan IDs
**            @RGUSERCHR2 Fee share ID
**            @RGUSERNUM1 n/a
**   RETURN:  Provides UX PERFORMSKIPAPAYMENT response
**
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**  Error codes and Logging Messages
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**  500: System in memo mode
**  501: Error reading/opening config file
**  502: Config file validation error
**  503: Invalid loan id
**  504: Attempt to skip a payment on an ineligible loan
**  505: Invalid fee share id
**  506: Loan Record Update Failed
**  507: Tracking Record Create Failed
**  508: Skip Pay Fee Post Failed
**
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**  Additional Information
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**
**  --------------------------------------------------------------------
**  Modification History:
**   Ver. 2.0.0  04/01/2026 R. Robison: Original V2 version of Loan Payment Skip PowerOn
**               * Feature set based on: BANNO.LOANPAYMENT.SKIP.V1.POW Ver. 1.3.1 02/19/2026: JKeenan – Banno
**                       
**    
*]
SYMCONNECT
STATELESS

TARGET=ACCOUNT

DEFINE
 #INCLUDE "RD.GETDATA.DEF"
